  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This sample shows how to create a simple movie playback app using the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " framework (not "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avkit"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "). The "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " objects that manage a playerâ€™s visual output donâ€™t present any playback controls. Use the sample to build your own playback controls that implement the functionality to play, pause, fast forward, rewind, and scrub through movies."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "level": 3,
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Play a Movie in Fast Forward or Reverse",
          "anchor": "3537249"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You set the playerâ€™s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1388846-rate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property to change the rate of playback. A value of 1.0 plays the movie at its natural rate. Setting the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "rate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to 0.0 is the same as pausing playback using the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1387895-pause"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method. Set the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1388846-rate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property to a number greater than 1.0 to fast forward, and to a number less than 0.0 to reverse."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In this sample, the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "playFastForward"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method adds as much as 2.0 to the current player "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1388846-rate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property, up to a maximum "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "rate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " value of 2.0, when the user taps the Fast Forward button in the UI."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeListing",
          "code": [
            "// Play fast forward no faster than 2.0.",
            "player.rate = min(player.rate + 2.0, 2.0)"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "3537241",
            "title": "Listing 1"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "playReverse"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method subtracts as much as 2.0 from the current player "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayer/1388846-rate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property, down to a minimum "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "rate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " value of â€“2.0, when the user taps the Play Reverse button in the UI."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeListing",
          "code": [
            "// Reverse no faster than -2.0.",
            "player.rate = max(player.rate - 2.0, -2.0)"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "3537242",
            "title": "Listing 2"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You determine whether the player item supports fast forward playback by using the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avplayeritem/1389096-canplayfastforward"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property. Similarly, you determine the type of reverse play supported by using:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "unorderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": true,
